    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2002 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six M96 powerplant, delivering linear power delivery and a visceral exhaust note through a 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and communicative steering feel. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp. A driver-focused specimen optimized for the purist.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
