      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who needs a smooth, worry-free drive. It\u2019s been well-loved, kept clean, and is totally ready to hit the road with you today. I've honestly enjoyed every mile in it, and I think you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
