    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This F87-generation M2 is a pinnacle of modern chassis tuning, powered by the N55B30T0 3.0L twin-scroll turbocharged inline-six. Mated to a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain delivers 365 hp and 343 lb-ft of overboost torque through an electronically controlled Active M Differential. The suspension features forged aluminum control arms and knuckles to reduce unsprung weight, ensuring surgical turn-in and high-speed lateral stability. While displaying minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity is superlative. The cooling system and bushings have been recently inspected, and the vehicle retains its factory-spec geometry. This is a driver-focused machine that prioritizes analog feedback and mechanical harmony.",
